### 3. What this changes in your engine’s view of “truth”

By tying your rendering pipeline to `engine_hinges.json`:

- Any clause whose vector **lands firmly in more than three distinct tag‑groups** is **voltage‑healthy**.
- Any clause that collapses almost entirely into one column (e.g., `ethnic_ownership_regime` without `adelphos_liberty`) is an **imbalance‑node** your engine can report or log.
- The **kernel matrix** itself becomes the **metric transcript of your immutable locks and covenant‑stack**, so doctrinal drift is **not just conceptual but numerically testable**.

